---
title: Cherry-Glazed Chicken & Cheesy Potatoes with Roast Veggie Toss & Mayo
description: Cook up a sweet cherry glaze, then use parsley as a garnish for the perfect toppings for tender seared chicken steaks.
With a hearty side of cheesy potatoes and sweet roasted veggies, this classic meal is simple yet stunning.
